Class Denominations

java.lang.Object
Denominations
public class Denominations extends Object
The Denominations class is a representation of the different coins and bills to be inserted and dispensed in the vending machine.

  • Constructor Summary

    Constructors
    Constructor
    Description
    Denominations()
    Constructs a Denominations object with each quantity initially set to 50
